	"notes": [
		{
			"id": "nB_CtfhmpYiV1Ozwh",
			"markdown": "Zombies are reanimated corpses. They have mottled, muddy green flesh, as wel as various deep and fatal-looking wounds."
		},
		{
			"id": "n2IuNE8QMf3q6HHHL",
			"markdown": "Possible Diseases: Ataxia, Brain Rot, Brown Rot, Collywobbles, Chilis, Dampworm, Droops, Greenspore, Rattles, Rockjoint, Rust Chancre, Serpiginous Demetnia, Swamp Fever, Witbane, Wither, Yellow Tick."
		},
